item.title: Jframe error with client
item.dc:creator: @Scape-JAVA Scape-JAVA
item.description:
@Scape-JAVA wrote:

You’re missing the byte code for the Jframe class, if you get errors while complying it’s because you’re missing Jframe.java

@echo off "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_##\bin\java" -Xmx512m -cp . Jframe 10 0 highmem members 32 pause

also replace the ## with your current java JDK version.
